title: This Week - S13E20 - 2015.02.26 - 468p x264
description:
POLITICAL: This Week
On: BBC 1 HD     
Date: Thursday 26th February 2015 
Time: 23:45 to 00:30 

Andrew Neil looks at MPs and second jobs with author and Conservative MEP Dan Hannan, who thinks being in parliament should come second to another career. The review of the week's films comes from the Mirror's Kevin Maguire, while Nick Hewer, from Countdown and The Apprentice, will look at ethics and morals in business. The panellists are Diane Abbott and Michael Portillo. Miranda Green also joins them to look back on the week. Crack open the Blue Nun and prepare to watch public service broadcasting at its best, talking bazookas with Diane in leather! Sadly no Molly though :(

Miranda Green tweets: "@TobyonTV: Portillo is going to start singing, 
'I got chills, they're multiplying...' #bbctw " Love this pic.
